INSTALL
-------
Run install.sh

LINE FOLLOWER
-------------
Launch nxcEditorGambas2.gambas, open LineFollower.nxc.
Open nxcSimulator.
Edit robot to use motor A for left wheel and B for right.
Edit robot to use sensorport 3 as light sensor.
Load a black curve as background (such as the built-in 680X680 Lines background).
Place robot close to right edge of the line. It will continue to follow right edge.
A screenshot of the LineFollower in action is saved in LineFollower.png
